Developed,by,Frondiz,Bugify,is,a,simple,issue,tracking,service,that,integrates,with,a,development,team,s,source,control,system,making,it,a,useful,bug,tracking,tool,Bugify,offers,additional,features,such,as,email,and,desktop,notifications,labels,project,wide,searchability,quick,software,updates,history,tracking,issue,linking,project,milestones,and,more,The,Bugify,API,can,also,extend,the,service,into,external,third,party,applications,Each,API,call,is,performed,with,a,per,user,authentication,method,and,can,be,called,with,GET,and,POST,methods,to,retrieve,and,edit,information,regarding,issues,milestones,users,project,data,and,more